response.overview: Pro wrestling is often synonymous with controversy so we asked you to vote on wrestling’s singular most controversial moment. Here are the top 5 as voted by YOU!  Why don’t we give the stars of pro wrestling a shot at saying what they think of each of your entries!  This hilarious new series takes the shoot-style DVD in a whole new direction! All interviews are brand new footage, seen here for the first time on Wrestling’s Most!
response.title: Wrestling’s Most…Controversial Moment
